itemDesc1: Chat2 iOS/ Android Support 7th Jul to 5 Aug

Following changes have been made:

1. Added 2 search options: All and Assorted Lectures
2. Using All, data will be searched only in subgroup (incl. right and left label) and display the result with Subgroup name and it's right label. Clicking on Subgroup name will open the link.
3. You can use this link with any group/subgroup with their id and it will display it's entire table (useful to share the specific subgroup table with student). It's format is:
                    http://fh.com/giml/search/result/{group_id}/{subgroup_id}
4. Using Assorted Lectures, data will be searched in all tables including only column type of 'text' and display the result with table.
5. Search bar layout has been improved with separate combo box for search option on left side.
6. Improved the layout to support mobile devices. (Tested on Android 5.1 with Chrome)
7. Made the GIML table responsive for mobile devices. Before it strip the texts if no. of columns doesn't fit the layout of mobile device. (Tested on Android 5.1 with Chrome)
8. In Theme Options -> Header & Top Bar -> Layout, don't embed the GIML Search Bar inside any VC shortcode, otherwise it will not display correctly on mobile device. (Tested on Android 5.1 with Chrome)
9. Updated the layout of GI-Quran with bottom bar separating arabic from w2w translation and updated it's layout a bit to support mobile device. (Tested on Android 5.1 with Chrome)
